"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-track-athletes-under-pressure-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 2 August 2024 07:46 am Akani Simbine will be targeting medals in the 100m and 4x100m events.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 126}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m and 4x100m events\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Anton Geyser/Gallo Images With swimmer Tatjana Smith having led the charge over the first week of the Olympic Games, the focus will shift to athletics for the second half of the showpiece as South Africa's track and field stars look to add to the nation's growing medal haul.\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.273831106366846e-18, \"text\": \"Geyser\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geyser\"}, {\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"score\": 0.9998041284704842, \"rank\": 0.00018638340140303509, \"text\": \"Gallo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gallo_Record_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999997858729104, \"rank\": 2.089036866502625e-07, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 171}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmer Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"the charge\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"the first week\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 267}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"the second half\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"the showpiece\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's growing medal haul\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While they missed out on a medal at the Tokyo Games three years ago - the first time since readmission that the country has not earned an athletics medal at the Olympics - the national track and field team will be confident of returning to the podium in Paris.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999890137589, \"rank\": 1.0986151777405779e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"readmission\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"an athletics medal\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"the national track and field team\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they might not have to wait long to bag a medal, with the squad expected to make an explosive start this weekend.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"an explosive start\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Middle-distance runnerPrudence Sekgodisowill be among the first track athletes to compete, as she goes in the first-round 800m heats at 7.25pm on Friday night, with her sights set on a potential medal in the final next week.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sekgodisowill\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"the first track athletes\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the first-round 800m\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday night\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential medal\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the final next week\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, long-distance runnerAdrian Wildschuttwill be the first athlete in SA colours with a chance for a medal in the 10 000m final on Friday evening (9.20pm).\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999998908606, \"rank\": 1.0552145775698922e-10, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"long-distance runnerAdrian Wildschuttwill\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"the first athlete\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10 000m\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday evening\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the real fireworks are expected on Saturday and Sunday whenAkani Simbineturns out in the men's 100m event.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the real fireworks\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday and Sunday whenAkani Simbineturns\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100m\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing in the top five in the short-sprint final at the last two editions of the Games, Simbine looks to be in the shape of his life, and he will be hungry for his first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the short-sprint final\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two editions\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"Simbine\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the shape\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final, if he gets that far, will be held at 9.50pm on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"9.50pm\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if he misses out in the individual 100m sprint, Simbine will have another chance for a spot on the podium when he anchors the men's 4x100m relay team later next week.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the individual 100m sprint\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"Simbine\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"another chance\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 4x100m relay team\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The SA squad will also be gunning for a medal in the men's 4x400m relay, which is expected to be anchored by world record holderWayde van Niekerk.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1772, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999998908606, \"rank\": 1.0552145775698922e-10, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 4x400m relay\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"world record holderWayde van Niekerk\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa's swimmers have done well, and the track and field athletes are under pressure now to perform at their best and keep the nation's medal tally rising.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1916, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999997858729104, \"rank\": 2.089036866502625e-07, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track and field athletes\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's medal tally\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the form they have shown this year is anything to go by, they should give SA fans a few more reasons to celebrate.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999998908606, \"rank\": 1.0552145775698922e-10, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"a few more reasons\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.999663576935595, \"rank\": 0.00031883211954482343, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2316, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Citizen\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"a Preferred Source\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"u